and management. Prentice Hall, Englewood Cliffs, New Jersey.

Posk, K. and E. Howland. 1946. Influence
of nitrate level and light intensity on the growth and production
of greenhouse roses. Proc. Amer. Soc. Hort. Sci. 47:446-450.

Wolfe, J. S., and R. F. Cotton. 1975.
Airflow and temperature distribution in greenhouses with fan ventilation.
Acta Hort 46:71-89.

